      <summary>Does it handle multi-staff and multi-location businesses?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Each staff member has their own schedule, services, and availability. Customers pick a location first, then a service, then a staff member, all in one booking flow.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can customers pay during booking?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Razorpay, Cashfree, PhonePe, and UPI payment links are integrated. You can set full payment, partial advance, or pay-at-venue per service type.</div>
